  "title": "Set Difference",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "The \\emph{set difference} $A \\setminus B$ is the set of elements in $A$ but\nnot in $B$:\n\\[\nA \\setminus B \\;=\\; \\{\\, x \\mid x \\in A \\land x \\notin B \\,\\}.\n\\]",
